<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ870722-0015 </DOCNO><HL> Who's News:Gleason Corp.</HL><DD> 07/22/87</DD><SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO><IN> WNEWS GLE </IN><DATELINE> GLEASON CORP. (Rochester, N.Y.)  </DATELINE><TEXT>    Donald D. Lennox andPaul W. MacAvoy were named directors of this maker of gearproduction equipment and automated manufacturing systems,increasing board membership to 10. Mr. Lennox is chairman andchief executive officer of Rochester-based Schlegel Corp. Mr.MacAvoy is dean and professor at the University ofRochester's William E. Simon Graduate School of Business andAdministration.</TEXT></DOC>